title: 784. Daniel Jeremiah's 2022 Pre-Draft Media Call
itunes:title: 784. Daniel Jeremiah's 2022 Pre-Draft Media Call
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a special new episode. DJ answered questions from the media on a two hour Zoom call. In this episode, catch the best of the call as the NFL Network analyst answers questions regarding the draft, team fits and all the prospects within it. All things NFL draft are covered on this year's media call!
